data.description: Welcome to this stunning three-bedroom, 3 bathrooms home nestled in the highly sought-after Charter Oaks neighborhood of Pensacola. Boasting a generous 1976 sq ft, this residence offers an abundance of space and luxurious features that are sure to impress.  Step inside and be greeted by the oversized master bedroom, a true retreat with ample room for relaxation. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like haven, complete with a jet tub for ultimate indulgence.   Entertain guests in style with the formal dining and living areas, perfect for hosting elegant dinner parties or special occasions. The spacious family room is adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings with loved ones.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a generous eat-in area and plenty of counter space for meal preparation. Adjacent to the family room, you'll find a small room that can be easily transformed into a home office or a dedicated space for homeschooling, providing flexibility and convenience.  The home's layout is thoughtfully designed, ensuring a seamless flow between rooms that inspires both privacy and unity. Each space is well-connected, allowing for effortless movement throughout the house.  Step outside into the spacious backyard, a perfect oasis for outdoor activities and relaxation. Whether you're hosting a summer barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this backyard offers endless possibilities for enjoyment and entertainment.  Located in the desirable Charter Oaks neighborhood, this home is surrounded by a sense of community and tranquility. With its convenient location, you'll have easy access to nearby amenities, schools, and shopping centers.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and elegance of this Pensacola gem.
